The App installer is an interface to install 3rd party applications like joomla, wordpress, phpbb on webhosting accounts. 

This is an auto installer program. Follow the steps to install applications through the App Installer.

- Install Application 
- Login to the client portal >> Go to Menu >> Apps
- At the top right click on the "Deploy an App"

- It will open the installation window. From that window you can select the website and location you want to install, username, password, email address, etc.
Complete the form and then click on the Install button. 

That's all. The installation will start automatically and send an email to the customer email address. 

**List/Edit/Update/Backup/Uninstall the Installed Applications 
**
- Go to App Installer through the client portal.
- Click on My Applications to list the installed application on that account.

- From there you can perform the update,edit,backup,clone and uninstall operations on the installed applications. Just select application from the list and click on the operation you want to do.

**Restore the Application from Backup
**
Customer can restore the applications from the backup they created through app installer. 

- Go to App Installer through the client portal.
- Click on My Backups to list the current backups. 
- Select the backup from the list and then click on the restore button.
